NAME: Hotels Booking
DESCRIPTION: This app allows you to choose your hotels and make early reservations. Transportation is provided whenever you need, with taxi rides or by renting cars.

NAME: Grocery Shopping
DESCRIPTION: You can use this app to buy you groceries. Search the needed items and add to the cart for purchase. The items will be delivered to your doorstep

NAME: Taxi Ride
DESCRIPTION: You can get taxi rides from any place you like to any destination. Just choose the locations on the map and a taxi would come to you. Pay online through the app or directly pay cash to the driver.
